Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The year just flew by, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have another good'un.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be biddin' farewell to some of y'all in three more months.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess who I'm talkin' about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean me, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can believe, right!? {Changed from 'I can't believe, right!?'  -xUOrchestra}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,People always talk about the New Year's mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I guess there's kind of a weird atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it changes the second school starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that New Year's wields a mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the fact that I spent the first three days of the year busy working at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...I gained weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,New Year's magic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The cold weather makes it difficult to burn off your fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I did a lot of moving around, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days of busy work as a shrine maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you ate just as much, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrine maiden. New Year's food!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrine maiden. Zoni soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrine maiden. Snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Snacks! Snacks! Snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrine maiden. Snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But the pictures of having fun during New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...usually include badminton...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...One Hundred Poets...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...and kite flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I've never actually seen someone do those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,These days, it's dangerous with stuff like electric lines and cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I just watched TV and read books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After those first three busy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I did those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed badminton, One Hundred Poets, and Pin the Tail on the Donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't match your image.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My family follows western customs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but our relatives in the country are more traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We wore kimonos and went to the temple on New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I had fun with my cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,An omnipotent god...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Way more Japanese than I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,More traditional than my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why Pin the Tail on the Donkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In One Hundred Poets...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're all 31 syllable poems, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You read out the first verse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...and look for the card with the rest of the poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The experts snatch up the cards in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand playing a game that makes you feel like you're studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,People like you who view mental games as a chore are why Japan's going down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't they use One Hundred Poets for like a card battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You could summon a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Think there was a Semimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Semimaru uses a shining attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono no Komachi uses a lovely strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that sound fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to your world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't more physical games have helped you lose weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was those stupid rice cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice cakes are loaded with calories, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One as big as a matchbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...is equivalent to a whole bowl of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that Kagami's eating a bowl of rice with each bite!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You also ate rice cakes, didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:14.81,Notes,,0,0,0,,[zoni soup: a broth eaten with rice cakes; New Year's meal]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom's gone, so I've rarely had zoni soup and that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't really eat rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With zoni soup, sweet red bean soup, soy flour rice cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many fun ways to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's gonna lose to the rice cakes again next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have to eat for New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...instead of rice cakes, Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff like pizza and pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Our year starts with raw pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad cleans out the pasta machine at the end of every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing rusts if you don't use it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use it without cleaning it first,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the pasta ends up all black and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So we clean it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...and make pasta and pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds very thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Kagami's house probably orders pizza and their pasta consists of cup noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,More like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have pizza or pasta on New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't go with traditional foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes great with roast chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a traditional New Year's food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Under western traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you have for New Year's, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family sounds all wealthy and western,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so you probably didn't have traditional stuff or rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you had a full course French dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate traditional foods...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I was unable to bite through a rice cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it stretched like whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this walking pillar to elements of moe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice cake goes whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But New Year's goes by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Winter break goes by fast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be a long vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but after cleaning, writing New Year's cards, and homework,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have much time to relax, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't do New Year's cards this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you copied my homework yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uguu~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have your first dream of the year, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it supposed to be a good omen if you dream about certain things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, it's one: Mt. Fuji, two: hawk, three: eggplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Officially, you would add...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...four: fan, five: tobacco, six: blind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes all the way up to six!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who ever dreams about that kind of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of dream would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And why a blind man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to dream about all of those at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If all of those showed up in your dreams, you'd be really blessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I believe that just one will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would have to dream about a hawk twice and an eggplant three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And quite frankly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who really remembers what they dream about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,People who care about that stuff are having way too much fun with New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In my first dream this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:07:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...I opened my shoe locker to find my shoes missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had no choice but to take shoes from someone else's open locker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the size was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked up the meaning of this dream in the encyclopedia for dream fortune telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it said that it's a sign I am pursuing skills useful to society...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it will take a while before I accomplish that goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The shoes apparently represent societal standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheesecake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...pretty ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I kinda understand, but kinda not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Another person was goofing off on the stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...during the coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they realize they're representing Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes you wonder why they even bother going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to go to a boring coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And this girl's gonna grow up to be a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys going to wear to your ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well go with a long-sleeve kimono...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's probably going to have me wear a long-sleeve kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see him doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When you wear one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'd look more like a little kid going to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope ya had fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, Yui-neesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my husband was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot happens during New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and my sister had a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a weak body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It definitely wasn't because I didn't give her any New Year's allowance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a cop would reveal what she was really thinking before I've said a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A One Hundred Poets tournament is currently under way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it's been one crazy ride so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do on New Year's when you were a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I did all kinds of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot. {Wasn't sure what to do here; having no gap felt odd so I just left it in -xUOrchestra}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She really just goes with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard her say anything serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I outgrew my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's always cooped up under the kotatsu these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotatsu are so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to the bathroom's a pain, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't say that so loudly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have a sure-fire way to get a person out of a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay under the kotatsu too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll get stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So your dad doesn't need a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He likes them as much as the next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause we've both fallen asleep together under the kotatsu before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But they say that you'll catch a cold if you fall asleep under a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So we turn it off once someone notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a mix of heaven and hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Like right before you turn it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,..and after you turn it off, it feels even colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And doesn't it really suck when you get out of bed in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're at it, it's totally freezing after you get undressed and before you get in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But not enough to make you run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You might slip and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And doesn't it suck when you need to go to the bathroom in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the trip from the bus to the classroom is also hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It always gets a lot more exciting this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It kinda tickles me how everyone can get so worked up every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Having someone special on this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...and confessing your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...and having them reciprocated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...is a beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just see it as a conspiracy by the chocolate industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you could say it's also a special time of year for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a sale on the unsold chocolate afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I'm looking for chocolate to use in making my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, you have no dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Money can't buy love! {Wasn't sure what to do here -xUOrchestra}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, that's what they like to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...but isn't Valentine chocolate a way of showing love through money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess someone who's only experienced love in games has some harsh views.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in games, it's all about upping your relationship level before the day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't do anything special for Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys dream too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody managed to trigger the Kagami flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm super popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When you talk about flags and relationship levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I seriously get worried about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't limit yourself to events in games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand those narrow-minded people who don't know what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, events only take a few hours in game time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...so Valentine's Day is usually over in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:53.31,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But this year, I'm planning on giving chocolate to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone playing the same online game as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend from your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving it to him in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not actually going to meet the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be in-game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the characters are still human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that even count?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just meant a game character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you insult my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're married in-game, and my character's male.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So the guy is giving the girl chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And wouldn't it be like a girl giving a girl chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If the other person's a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The other person's a guy in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it doesn't matter as long as you're having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yesterday, Miyuki-san was, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Females giving chocolates on February 14th is a Japanese custom."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san! {Not sure how to do styles, so I just stuck it under note -xUOrchestra}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In western society, people of both genders...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...give chocolate and cards to friends and people they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...so a girl like me could still get lots of chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could interpret it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you sure have a lot of confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you already know for a fact that you'll be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In foreign countries, little girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No risqué statements allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you accept this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible wrapping...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...for a uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And the inside's all cool and heart-shaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I put some effort into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's always enthusiastic about this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She was making them until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't give any friendship chocolate to guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll definitely get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami's giving me chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa was making hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I just joined in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami's looking like she's good at everything when she actually sucks, so when she secretly works hard, it turns me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.46,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Zip it! {Same as before -xUOrchestra}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, it's just a friends thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry the shape's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The shape isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is that you made it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time's most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you give anybody chocolate, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave chocolate to my father and a relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave chocolate to everybody I'm friendly with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave chocolate to you, Tsukasa, and Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys sure had a boring St. Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't need to hear it from someone who lives in an online game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cousin was accepted to Ryouou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty far from her home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...so she'll be living with us starting next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always been like a little sister, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...so we've been in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...nobody would be able to tell who's younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like a little sister in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's that small!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she got accepted to our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...your cousin must be really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That just sounds like you're being really presumptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're a student here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I barely passed the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Exams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking our exams next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll be spending the whole year studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I even take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even picked a major.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You seriously need to start thinking about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying, manual labor, and me just don't mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of future do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:46.04,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I design games. 'Cause it's my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Use a hobby to make a profit and make games...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a self-proclaimed manga artist who can only sell at Comiket...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.04,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Megas smoked cheese-nyoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.42,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,There can only be one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps, indulge your curiosity and become a professional writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.04,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,And this isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, maybe just a novelist who aims for a niche market.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you like computers, I guess art design might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a scenario writer who uses random material instead of an actual story writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Or she doesn't go to college...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or they're all the same thing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Legendary Girl A...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She shook us off last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We will absolutely make sure she reaches the goal known as our register!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Giro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then allow us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...help her find her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let 'er rip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempting to determine Legendary Girl A's objective for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Countin' on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the newest comic out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Volume 14 of Sgt. Frog, sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise the height of our goods to the appropriate level...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...to bring them to the attention of Legendary Girl A!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And deploy the flyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Deployment complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on her movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And as Legendary Girl A approaches the register...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...deploy our best-selling goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Legendary Girl A's objective isn't the comics section!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch target to the DVD section.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...block all side paths so Legendary Girl A...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...heads straight to the new DVD section!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama! Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gero-gero-gero-gero build-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.82,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Tama-tama-tama-tam build-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...picked up the item!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally become a winner today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us have a wild celebration tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a feint!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to bring out my trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring that bargain, super-rare, out-of-print DVD to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She is heading for the register.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The crowd inside me is cheering with applause right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your total comes to 1,785 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm short 3 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please put that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's kick this into gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already on the thirteenth episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As you already know, I'm your navigator, Kogami Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Akira-sama's assistant, Shiraishi Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:37.30,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.54,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:41.32,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on episode 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Into the second season.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we've reached the fifth station on Mt. Fuji, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.26,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.17,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:47.09,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.74,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can drive up to the fifth station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've climbed Mt. Takao before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have something else to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:03.26,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mah, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama's twin drills look wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so wonderful about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The way they go round and round like a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a special announcement today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The results for the Lucky Star figure poll!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have Akira-sama announce the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The characters that will soon be getting figures are Izumi Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.90,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama, do a proper job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, everybody knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.28,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just means that the higher-ups think the actual show is more important than this corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The producers agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just fall for your little trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already used to being backstabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Little trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an awful thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't tell me that it says you're going to have a figure made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:20:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be making a figure of Izumi Konata-san this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And the popular Shiraishi Minoru will also get a figure!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So please send us any suggestions or comments you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave them on our home page.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:22.02,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:27.32,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:29.00,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,All the staff members can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Drill!
