Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:41.82,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} F-F-F-Forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.61,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:47.07,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Forgot my something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:56.66,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} That fragment of memory I left behind on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:22:01.42,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} It's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:05.09,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Along with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:10.26,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} The red sunset was so brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:14.18,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} On Romantic Jougashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:23.48,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Go ahead and laugh at me for being an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:33.06,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} That's how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:39.64,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:48.59,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Every now and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:59.02,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} ...give me a gentle embrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, next time on Sgt. Frog:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, next time on Lucky Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Giro-giro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrade, I have a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese anime is now a global industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we use it to brainwash the people on Pekopon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...we can complete the invasion of Pekopon in no time, sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a genius, Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.99,0:23:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A solider should act like a soldier and use brute force!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth, you red dharma doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In this age, whoever controls information controls the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your prehistoric mind wouldn't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You better watch yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.25,0:23:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Under One Roof."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gero!
